      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>An order of <persName ref="#shamsalDin">Shamsuddin</persName> to <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> to stop disturbing the conditions in district
               (pargana) <placeName ref="#hindola">Hindola</placeName>. The order details the complaint of <persName ref="#surajBhan">Suraj Bhan</persName> against <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam
                  Das</persName>, who held the position of landlord (chaudri) of <placeName ref="#hindola">Hindola</placeName> in partnership with him. <persName ref="#surajBhan">Suraj Bhan</persName> alleged
               that <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> had failed to share the perquisites of the position and had
               desolated a village.</p>
         </abstract>
